2019-07-19T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/safe_motoring_guides/driving_offence_points_system/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Fsafe_motoring_guides%2Fdriving_offence_points_system%2Findex.html&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=5a3a1eb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/safe_motoring_guides/driving_offence_points_system/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n依到佢個計法係違例日期，唔係定罪日期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1e666f56734fe30cab1937f3e450a5cef23bc55","tid":1331244,"uid":223079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15ac66f27d6ac6e47e1ade9192b961639cc57f91","tid":1331244,"uid":44728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"250990e91285fcd330e5e2bcbfba4a738f34647a","tid":1331244,"uid":223079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b683d8b53eaaea8ce705d4e205cff5dd4325e43","tid":1331244,"uid":44728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T08:08:30.000Z","msg":"唔係計案發日期咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:31:18.000Z","msg":"我四月底被周到衰老不，之後問咗運輸署，佢話個法官（數個月之後判）之前，不會扣分罰錢喎。<br />\n<br />\n所以我先認為係計定罪果日咁了<br />\n<br />\n無上網睇過，但如有錯請指定"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T10:47:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/safe_motoring_guides/driving_offence_points_system/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.td.gov.hk%2Ftc%2Froad_safety%2Fsafe_motoring_guides%2Fdriving_offence_points_system%2Findex.html&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDS9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=5a3a1eb4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.td.gov.hk/tc/road_safety/safe_motoring_guides/driving_offence_points_system/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n依到佢個計法係違例日期，唔係定罪日期 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:41:43.000Z","msg":"睇咗，不過我又唔係好同意：<br />\n<br />\n第一點：<br />\n&quot;違例駕駛記分制度在 1984 年 8 月 25 日實施。由該日開始，駕駛者如觸犯這制度所規定的任何違例事項，在下列情況<span style=\"color: red;\">即會被記分</span>：<br />\n<br />\n（甲） <span style=\"color: red;\">法庭裁定駕駛者罪名成立</span>；或<br />\n（乙） 駕駛者須繳付定額罰款。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n我明，但如果係按你所說咁，（甲）的情況通常跟違例唔係同一日（如老不就隔半年），即係話扣分由定罪果日生效啦，咁至於生效嘅意思係咪咁刁鑽追溯返違例果日，上面紅筆的寫法又唔似喎....<br />\n<br />\n第二點：<br />\n<br />\n三個計法例子係違例日期我看到，但由於建基於（甲）的定義去看，法庭未判都未扣分喎。三個計法例子出現&quot;違例日期&quot;的字眼如果改返&quot;定罪日期&quot;的話，咁同第一點的條文就呼應好多喇。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果我又ON 9咗錯誤解讀請指正。"},{"pid":"464da214f5862c49050c8f5468cea0b2c355feae","tid":1331244,"uid":223079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T11:55:03.000Z","msg":"再睇返，我覺得果三個例子入面的「被記分數」同「違例日期」咁對照法唔恰當/有誤導，因為咁樣就address唔到（<span style=\"color: red;\">甲） 法庭裁定駕駛者罪名成立</span>一項。 除非法廷判罪扣分係追回到違例果日計起，但邊有咁SO呀。<br />\n<br />\n有錯隨便插"},{"pid":"7322ab46d8741bbe4341274f27069509a72e570c","tid":1331244,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6b695bdc43ba0efbc3552a6961a52eb7d924ed3","tid":1331244,"uid":283433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:02:33.000Z","msg":"會有信寄過嚟,會顯示扣分時間.<br />\n最後扣分時間計兩年唔好中分就Clear."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:52:13.000Z","msg":"On99"},{"pid":"6b91eee1e4f24d88d610d68f2692e80cb1a52eac","tid":1331244,"uid":18241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:54:15.000Z","msg":"違例日期起計兩年"}]}